# Shadcn & Radix Usage

## Component Usage
- Use Shadcn UI components for forms, dialogs, and navigation.
- Use Radix primitives for accessibility and keyboard navigation.

## Customization
- Extend Shadcn components via props and Tailwind classes.
- Avoid direct DOM manipulation; use provided APIs.

## Accessibility
- Ensure all interactive elements are accessible via keyboard.
- Use ARIA attributes where required.
